title: Amazing 1 Bedroom Apartment
posting_body: ['1339 S Ogden Dr Los Angeles, CA 90019', 'Beautiful 2 Bedroom Apartment.', 'Stainless appliances, New Appliances, Flooring and Fixtures.', 'Deposit 1 Month based on approved credit.', 'Large Spacious Layout, Great interior storage, A/C and much more.', 'This property is situated in the Mid-City area of Los Angeles, you will find the heart of Koreatown, Wilshire/Western, and heading in the other direction you have The Grove and Beverly Center and a 7 min walk from La Pico Plaza.', "There are also five parks within 5.6 miles, including La Brea Tar Pits, Zimmer Children's Museum, and Kenneth Hahn State Recreation Area.", 'You would be situated perfectly near the Pico/Rimpau station and for drivers you are minutes away from the 10 and 110 freeways for better convenience.', 'Community Features:', 'Parking area and On-site Laundry Room.', 'Also access to Appfolio an Online Resident Portal to conveniently', 'Pay Online, Request Maintenance Services Online, Check your balance any time, and communicate services.', 'Ernest', 'show contact info']
